0Real%20IDs%20starting%20May%207.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETravelers%20without%20Real%20IDs%20could%20face%20delays%20or%20be%20barred%20from%20entering%20security%20checkpoints.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ETravelers%20in%20the%20United%20States%20could%20have%20their%20vacations%20derailed%20this%20summer%20if%20they%20don't%20secure%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-id-deadline-dmv-women-face-chaos-marriage-certificate-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReal%20ID%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20May%207%20deadline%20set%20by%20Homeland%20Security%20is%20fast%20approaching%2C%20meaning%20adults%20boarding%20domestic%20flights%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20able%20to%20use%20their%20old%20driver's%20licenses%20as%20identification.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20happens%20if%20you%20arrive%20at%20a%20TSA%20security%20checkpoint%20without%20a%20Real%20ID%3F%20Here's%20everything%20you%20need%20to%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d69eb945-03ef-4c1a-9504-ee39544dc01e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20a%20Real%20ID%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EReal%20IDs%20were%20a%20recommendation%20by%20the%209%2F11%20Commission%2C%20formed%20in%202002%20under%20former%20President%20George%20W.%20Bush%2C%20for%20the%20federal%20government%20to%20%26quot%3Bset%20standards%20for%20the%20issuance%20of%20sources%20of%20identification%2C%20such%20as%20driver's%20licenses%20and%20identification%20cards.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20boarding%20domestic%20commercial%20flights%2C%20Real%20IDs%20will%20be%20required%20to%20grant%20access%20to%20certain%20federal%20facilities%20and%20nuclear%20power%20plants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Congress%20formally%20passed%20the%20Real%20ID%20Act%20in%202005.%20However%2C%20the%20federal%20government%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-id-deadline-air-travel-delayed-2025-drivers-license-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edelayed%20enforcing%20Real%20IDs%3C%2Fa%3E%20several%20times%20over%20the%20last%20two%20decades.%20Although%20Real%20IDs%20are%20a%20form%20of%20identification%2C%20Homeland%20Security%20said%20they%20are%20not%20considered%20proof%20of%20citizenship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228cd3c42d-4247-4584-a90f-cd1d9a3e5cde%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20you%20know%20if%20you%20have%20a%20Real%20ID-compliant%20card%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226318%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20example%20of%20ab%20Texas%20REAL%20ID.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6817c3f23fe8d3928364e22d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224263%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20example%20of%20a%20Texas%20Real%20ID%20card.%3Cp%3EUSA%20TODAY%20Network%20via%20Reuters%20Connect%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20previous%20ID%20cards%2C%20a%20Real%20ID%20will%20have%20a%20star%20marking%20on%20the%20upper%20half%20of%20the%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20card%20does%20not%20have%20a%20star%20marking%2C%20it%20is%20not%20REAL%20ID-compliant%20and%20won't%20be%20accepted%20as%20proof%20of%20identity%20to%20board%20commercial%20aircraft%2C%26quot%3B%20Homeland%20Security%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20are%20variations.%20Depending%20on%20the%20state%2C%20Real%20IDs%20can%20feature%20a%20gold%20star%2C%20a%20black%20star%2C%20a%20gold%20circle%20with%20a%20white%20star%20cutout%2C%20or%20a%20black%20circle%20with%20a%20white%20star%20cutout.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20California%2C%20Real%20IDs%20have%20an%20image%20of%20a%20gold%20grizzly%20bear%20with%20a%20white%20star%20cutout.%20Homeland%20Security%20announced%20on%20April%2024%20that%20New%20York%20State%20Real%20IDs%2C%20enhanced%20licenses%2C%20and%20identification%20cards%20will%20have%20a%20star%20or%20the%20US%20flag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221bec5dea-f866-4266-8d77-0226c5a43704%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20you%20get%20a%20Real%20ID%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20of%20acquiring%20a%20Real%20ID%20varies%20by%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20obtaining%20a%20Real%20ID%20in%20Alaska%20means%20applying%20in%20person%20at%20an%20Alaska%20Department%20of%20Motor%20Vehicles%20office%20and%20providing%20a%20primary%20document%20showing%20specific%20information%2C%20including%20birth%20name%20and%20US%20citizenship%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Texas%2C%20people%20can%20apply%20for%20a%20Real%20ID-compliant%20card%20in%20person%20at%20a%20Texas%20Department%20of%20Public%20Safety%20office.%20Some%20may%20be%20eligible%20to%20renew%20their%20driver's%20license%20or%20ID%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20very%20least%2C%20Homeland%20Security%20said%20people%20must%20show%20documents%20showing%20their%20full%20legal%20name%2C%20date%20of%20birth%2C%20Social%20Security%20number%2C%20two%20proofs%20of%20principal%20residence%20address%2C%20and%20legal%20status%2C%20to%20obtain%20a%20Real%20ID.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Business%20Insider%20has%20reported%2C%20some%20people%20who%20have%20changed%20their%20names%20via%20marriage%20or%20divorce%20are%20having%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-id-deadline-dmv-women-face-chaos-marriage-certificate-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrouble%20gathering%20the%20necessary%20paperwork%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20apply%20for%20Real%20ID.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHomeland%20Security's%20website%20provides%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dhs.gov%2Freal-id%3Futm_source%3Dgoogle%26utm_medium%3Dcpc%26utm_adgroup%3D%7BAdGroupName%7D%26utm_campaign%3D%7BCampaignName%7D%26gad_source%3D1%26gad_campaignid%3D21447596778%26gbraid%3D0AAAAABq_W-SsHgFPFvtSKxqWoqBBa4Lms%26gclid%3DCj0KCQjwoNzABhDbARIsALfY8VOf_NNEjiPzGMp4t_04CU5Gl1obFANrpPtzerGcRaXykeIuNTH5I8caAncAEALw_wcB%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReal%20ID%20map%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20allowing%20users%20to%20click%20on%20their%20state%20for%20more%20information.%3C%2F