rtner's%20view%20is%20valid%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it's%20still%20worth%20supporting%20her%20dreams.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGot%20a%20question%20for%20our%20columnist%3F%20Write%20to%20For%20Love%20%26amp%3B%20Money%20using%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdhFnAxR57cNtGiwNUd-6vLAYAc75grvly3C10-854vFP4arw%2Fviewform%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%20Google%20form%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EDear%20For%20Love%20%26amp%3B%20Money%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20daughter%20wants%20to%20play%20the%20cello.%20I%20couldn't%20be%20more%20thrilled.%20She%20is%20signed%20up%20for%20orchestra%20this%20fall%2C%20and%20they%20will%20loan%20her%20an%20instrument%2C%20but%20I%20would%20rather%20buy%20her%20a%20cello%20now%20and%20have%20her%20take%20lessons%20over%20the%20summer%20to%20help%20her%20really%20fall%20in%20love%20with%20it.%20She%20agrees%20and%20even%20has%20her%20eye%20on%20a%20beautiful%20white%20one.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20partner%20thinks%20we're%20being%20ridiculous%20and%20rushing%20into%20something%20that%20will%20end%20up%20being%20a%20short%20phase.%20The%20cello%20she%20wants%20is%20only%20%24250%2C%20so%20their%20stubbornness%20feels%20like%20it's%20about%20more%20than%20just%20the%20money.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20feel%20like%20my%20partner%20is%20being%20a%20miser%20and%20pinching%20pennies%20because%20they%20don't%20believe%20in%20our%20girl.%20How%20can%20I%20help%20them%20see%20the%20investment%20this%20could%20be%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ESincerely%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EMarried%20to%20a%20Miser%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDear%20Married%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20can%20try%20to%20get%20at%20the%20real%20reason%20your%20partner%20is%20resistant%20to%20spending%20money%2C%20but%20all%20we%20can%20know%20for%20sure%20is%20what%20they%20are%20telling%20you%20%E2%80%94%20they%20don't%20think%20your%20daughter%20is%20serious%20enough%20about%20the%20instrument%20to%20justify%20the%20cost.%20I%20can%20see%20why%20you%20might%20interpret%20this%20as%20%26quot%3Bthey%20don't%20believe%20in%20our%20girl%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20that%20is%20likely%20an%20oversimplification%20of%20an%20opinion%20I'm%20sure%20holds%20a%20lot%20of%20nuance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20I%20was%20eight%2C%20I%20took%20piano%20lessons%20for%20two%20years%20and%20learned%20very%20little%3B%20then%20I%20watched%20a%20dueling%20fiddle%20act%20at%20Silver%20Dollar%20City%20and%20begged%20my%20parents%20for%20a%20violin%2C%20which%20my%20dad%20agreed%20to.%20I%20began%20my%2018-month%20career%20as%20a%20violinist%2C%20which%20ended%20when%20I%20told%20my%20mom%20that%20the%20strain%20of%20holding%20the%20instrument%20aloft%20was%20too%20great%20for%20my%20scrawny%20little%20arm.%20Later%2C%20I%20begged%20my%20dad%20for%20a%20guitar%2C%20and%20I%20received%20a%20beautiful%20Alvarez%20guitar%20for%20my%2016th%20birthday.%20I%20was%20over%20it%20by%20my%2017th.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20don't%20share%20this%20story%20because%20I'm%20rolling%20my%20eyes%20at%20your%20daughter's%20aspirations%20or%20siding%20with%20your%20partner.%20I%20only%20share%20it%20because%20we%20all%20have%20similar%20stories%20from%20our%20childhood.%20My%20guess%20is%2C%20your%20partner%20has%20a%20story%20of%20their%20own.%20We%20don't%20just%20make%20these%20predictions%20about%20our%20kids%20from%20a%20place%20of%20judgment%3B%20often%2C%20we%20make%20them%20based%20on%20what%20we%20know%20about%20ourselves.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20insignificant%20as%20%24250%20may%20seem%20to%20you%2C%20your%20spouse%20could%20view%20it%20differently.%