20machine%2C%20which%20will%20bake%20them%20too%2C%20making%20the%20entire%20process%20fully%20automated.%20%E2%80%9CI%20want%20it%20to%20be%20easy%20and%20convenient%20for%20my%20customers.%20Everything%20should%20come%20from%20the%20machine%2C%20both%20the%20%3Cem%3Echhole%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekulcha%3C%2Fem%3E.%20That%E2%80%99s%20the%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98What%20if%20this%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20work%3F%20What%20if%20I%20fail%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20discussing%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F285107%2Fengineer-couple-builds-electric-bull-for-farm-maintenance-work-help-marginalised-farmers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexperience%20of%20building%20a%20machine%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20juggling%20time%20as%20a%20full-time%20banker%2C%20the%20entrepreneur%20shares%20the%20countless%20moments%20of%20doubt%20and%20failure.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20no%20idea%20how%20to%20build%20a%20vending%20machine.%20There%20were%20times%20I%20thought%2C%20%E2%80%98What%20if%20this%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20work%3F%20What%20if%20I%20fail%3F%E2%80%99%20But%20I%20kept%20pushing%20forward%20and%20got%20motivated%20by%20little%20wins%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20entrepreneur%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20to%20learn%20everything%20from%20scratch%2C%20and%20it%20was%20exhausting%2C%20but%20I%20was%20focused%20on%20achieving%20my%20goal.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20that%20determination%20is%20paying%20off.%20Chakh%20De%20Chole%20officially%20launched%20at%20two%20outlets%20in%20Delhi%20%E2%80%94%20one%20in%20Vikaspuri%20and%20the%20other%20in%20Rajouri%20Garden%20%E2%80%94%20in%20December%202024.%20The%20vending%20machine%20has%20become%20an%20instant%20hit%2C%20providing%20fresh%20%3Cem%3Echhole%20kulche%3C%2Fem%3E%20with%20the%20same%20authentic%20taste%20to%20every%20customer.%20Sagar%20is%20now%20planning%20to%20expand%20to%20other%20cities%20like%20Jaipur%20and%20Bengaluru%2C%20with%20more%20machines%20on%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20been%20getting%20inquiries%20from%20places%20like%20Norway%2C%20Canada%2C%20and%20Dubai%2C%20but%20for%20now%2C%20I%20want%20to%20focus%20on%20building%20the%20brand%20in%20India.%20There%20is%20a%20lot%20to%20do%20here%20first%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi-based%20Rajat%20Kapur%2C%20a%20Chartered%20Accountant%2C%20recalls%20his%20first%20visit%20to%20the%20Rajouri%20Garden%20outlet%2C%20%E2%80%9CAt%20first%2C%20I%20was%20a%20bit%20hesitant%20about%20whether%20%3Cem%3Echhole%20kulche%3C%2Fem%3E%20from%20a%20vending%20machine%20could%20capture%20the%20real%20taste%20and%20flavour.%20But%20I%20was%20genuinely%20surprised.%20The%20taste%20was%20spot%20on%2C%20better%20than%20I%20expected.%20I%20have%20already%20been%20to%20the%20outlet%20twice%2C%20and%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20get%20enough%20of%20it.%20The%20spices%20are%20perfectly%20blended%2C%20and%20the%20best%20part%20is%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20ready%20in%20just%2060%20seconds%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20so%20convenient.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20quick%20and%20delicious%20meal%20that%20has%20made%20a%20place%20in%20my%20heart.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20heart%20behind%20Chakh%20De%20Chole%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20banker%20credits%20the%20venture%E2%80%99s%20success%20to%20his%20family.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F406059%2Fsubramani-kho-kho-world-cup-journey-tamil-nadu-sports%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efamily%20has%20been%20incredibly%20supportive%3C%2Fa%3E.%20My%20mother%2C%20especially%2C%20was%20a%20huge%20inspiration%20for%20me.%20When%20I%20told%20her%20I%20wanted%20to%20quit%20banking%20and%20do%20something%20of%20my%20own%2C%20she%20did%20not%20hesitate%20to%20back%20me%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sagar%20says.