%2FTBI-featured-image-17_11zon-1-1746188875.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Consultation%20in%20collaboration%20with%20CII%5Cn%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-17_11zon-1-1746188875.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-17_11zon-1-1746188875-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-17_11zon-1-1746188875-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-17_11zon-1-1746188875-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-17_11zon-1-1746188875-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-424650%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EConsultation%20in%20collaboration%20with%20CII%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20scale%20up%20the%20efforts%2C%20Sanhita%20identified%20grassroots%20women%20leaders%20(called%20champions)%20from%20the%20workers%20group%2C%20who%20are%20now%20mobilising%20others%2C%20building%20awareness%2C%20and%20advocating%20for%20safer%20workplaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlongside%20this%2C%20Sanhita%20works%20with%20trade%20unions%2C%20Employers%E2%80%99%20Associations%20and%20the%20Labour%20Department%20to%20improve%20institutional%20accountability.%C2%A0As%20a%20result%20of%20Sanhita%E2%80%99s%20continuous%20engagement%20with%20trade%20unions%20in%20the%20jute%20industry%2C%20both%20central%20and%20mill-based%2C%20over%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20Sexual%20Harassment%20of%20Women%20at%20Workplace%20related%20demands%20were%20included%20in%20the%20Charter%20of%20Demands%20of%20Jute%20Mill%20Workers%20during%202022%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20the%20history%20of%20trade%20unions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20